    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine domini Dei nostri Iesu Christi regis aeterni. <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/79">Hugo</persName> et <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/72">Lotharius</persName> divina favente
                        clementia <rs key="#Emperor/king">reges</rs>. Regni nostri statum ad hoc
                        proficere credimus, si Aecclesiarum Dei tutores existimus earumque predia
                        usquequaque continuis augmentis dilatare curamus. Quocirca noverit omnium
                        fidelium sanctae Dei aecclesiae nostrorumque presentium scilicet ac
                        futurorum industria, <persName key="#Intercessory #Bishops #fidelisOf"><name
                                ref="Ambrosius">Ambrosium</name></persName> egregium <rs
                            key="#Bishops">presulem</rs> atque <persName
                            key="#Intercessory #Count #fidelisOf"><name ref="Lisiardus"
                                >Lisiardum</name></persName> gloriosum <rs key="#Count">comitem</rs>
                        dilectosque <rs key="#fidelisOf">fideles</rs> nostros suppliciter nostram
                            <rs key="#Intercessory">postulasse clementiam</rs>, quatenus <rs
                            key="#Curtes">cortem</rs> unam <rs key="#Fiscal_property">iuris
                            proprietatis nostre</rs>, fundatam in <rs key="#Fines">confinio</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/105">Placentini <rs
                                key="#Comitatus">comitatus</rs></geogName>, quae <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Inflow #Gift #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2044">Landasi</geogName> dicitur, et nobis obvenit per <rs
                            key="#Cartula #Offersio/donatio #Fiscal_property #Inflow #Gift">cartulam
                            donationis</rs> ab <persName key="#Bishops"><name ref="Ardingus"
                                >Ardingo</name></persName>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/96">venerabili <placeName ref="#places/38"
                                >Mutinensis</placeName> aecclesiae</orgName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">presule</rs>, ob amorem Dei ac pro nostrae parentumque
                        nostrorum animae salute <orgName key="#Curtes" ref="#juridical_persons/253"
                            >sanctissimo Antonino martiri Christi ac sacratissimae Iustinae
                            virgini</orgName> hoc nostrae auctoritatis precepto cum omni eiusdem
                        curtis integritate <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >iure proprietario concedere</rs> dignaremur. Quorum peticionibus
                        acclinati <rs key="#sonOf">karissimique filii nostri</rs>
                        <persName key="#Bishops #sonOf" ref="#people/1531">Bosonis</persName>
                        venerabilis <rs key="#Bishops">episcopi</rs> fidelitatem cognoscentes
                        continuam, qui iam nominati Beati Antonini Christi martiris ac Sanctae
                        Iustinae virginis aecclesiae pontifex fore cernitur, prescriptam cortem,
                        adiacentem in confinio iam prenominati Placentini comitatus, quae Landasi
                        dicitur, pro Dei amore nostreque animae salute seu parentum nostrorum
                        animarum remedio iam sepe dicto Christi martiri Antonino et B[e]atae virgini
                        Iustinae in integrum propri[e]tario iure per hoc nostrum regale preceptum
                        perpetuo concedimus ac largimur, et de nostro iure ac potestate in eorum ius
                        et potestatem omnino transfundimus ac delegamus una cum <rs key="#Houses"
                            >casis</rs>, <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs>, <rs key="#Wine"
                            >vineis</rs>, <rs key="#Cereals">campis</rs>, <rs key="#Hay/fodder"
                            >pratis</rs>, <rs key="#Landed_possessions">pascuis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Forests">silvis</rs>, <rs>salectis</rs>, <rs>sacionibus</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Rivers">aquis aquarumque decursibus</rs>, <rs key="#Mills"
                            >molendinis</rs>, <rs key="#Fisheries">piscationibus</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Royal_slave">servis et ancillis</rs>, <rs key="#Royal_aldius"
                            >aldionibus et aldianis</rs>, <rs key="#Mountains">montibus</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Natural_landscape">vallibus</rs>, <rs key="#Natural_landscape"
                            >planiciebus</rs>, <rs key="#Landed_possessions">coltis et
                        incoltis</rs>, <rs key="#Landed_possessions">divisis et indivisis</rs>,
                            <rs>ripis</rs>, <rs>rupinis</rs> omnibusque quae dici aut nominari
                        possunt ad eandem cortem pertinentibus vel aspicientibus; quatenus
                        pretaxatus Boso reverendus antistes dilectusque filius noster suique
                        successores predictam cortem cum omni sua integritate perpetualiter habeant,
                        teneant, possideant faciantque ex omnibus quae sibi iuste et legaliter
                        pertinuerint et quicquid illorum decreverit voluntas, absque contradictione
                        vel molestia seu minoratione cuiusque. Si quis igitur hoc nostre regalis
                        concessionis preceptum infringere vel inrumpere quandoque temtaverit, sciat
                        se compositurum <rs key="#Penalty">auri obtimi libras ducentas</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Camera_regis">medietatem camere nostre</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Camera_of_other_public_authorities">medietatem cui ex his omnibus
                            iniusta fuerit iniecta molestia</rs>. Quod ut verius credatur
                        diligentiusque futuris temporibus ab omnibus observetur, manu propria
                        roborantes de anulo nostro subter sigillari iussimus. Signa serenissimorum
                        (M) (M) Hugonis et Lotharii regum. <persName key="#Chancellor"
                            ref="#people/1535">Giseprandus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Chancellor">cancellarius</rs> iussu regum recognovi et subscripsi
                        (SR). Data V idus mar., anno dominicae incarnationis DCCCCXLV, regni vero
                        domni Hugonis piissimi regis XVIIII, Lotharii vero XIIII, indic. III. Actum
                            <placeName ref="#places/65">Papia</placeName>. Feliciter, amen.</ab>
                </div>
